  "description": "Add Preschool-Themed Hero Background to About Us Page\n\nImplement a hero section background on the About Us page that matches the visual style and playful aesthetic of the main page's hero section.\n\nRequirements:\n- Review the existing hero background implementation on the main/home page\n- Identify the design elements that create the \"preschool-like\" aesthetic (colors, shapes, patterns, illustrations)\n- Create or adapt a hero background for the About Us page using similar visual elements\n- Ensure the background complements the About Us page content without overwhelming text readability\n- Maintain consistent design language (color palette, illustration style, spacing) with the main page\n- Ensure responsive behavior across different screen sizes (mobile, tablet, desktop)\n- Optimize images/graphics for web performance\n- Verify sufficient contrast between background and foreground text for accessibility\n\nEdge Cases to Consider:\n- Text overlay readability in different viewport sizes\n- Background behavior when About Us content is shorter or longer than expected\n- Loading states for background images/graphics\n- Browser compatibility for any CSS effects or SVG elements used",
